agraph","text":"他们“白天里讲些冠提堂皇的语，暗夜","index":41,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"c96c003cde","type":"paragraph","text":"二里进行一些离间，挑拨，处裂的刻当”②","index":42,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"1919a00d8d","type":"paragraph","text":"他们“拉大旗作为览皮，包着自己，去","index":43,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"96f0b6a166","type":"paragraph","text":"周扬们知道，他们这一段见不得人的历吓呼别人；小不如意，就倚势（！）定人罪名，","index":44,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"0b0cfa7a61","type":"paragraph","text":"史，对于他们进行资本主义复降活动，是很面且重得可拍”，“横暴您肆，达于极点③。","index":45,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"d89ac52dda","type":"paragraph","text":"不利的，因而总是想复改，想翻案。他们等","index":46,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"253809257f","type":"paragraph","text":"了二十一年，终于在一九五七年反右派斗争","index":47,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"c8aefa4d5a","type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅着重指出，凡此种种，根子是在周扬们的“指导”，“他们自有一伙，狼狐为好，把持着文学界，弄得乌烟寿气。”④","index":48,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"d184463d24","type":"paragraph","text":"16@《鲁迅书简》下所，人民文学山版社1952","index":49,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"a1abd8e1ed","type":"paragraph","text":"年版，第780、975、775、975页。对于周扬们的这些险恶行径，鲁迅是深","index":50,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"ae04ca33eb","type":"paragraph","text":"您《鲁迅全集》第6卷，人民文学出版社1958年","index":51,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"d968c61dd6","type":"paragraph","text":"中了周扬们的投降主义文艺路线的要害，使中，找到了机会。","index":52,"publicationId":"5ba19c54-124b-4e05-bf76-73e558230021","articleId":"9fd48b042e"},{"id":"47ef6d913a